vote.title: An ordinance amending Ordinance No. 31287, previously approved on August 28, 2019, as amended by Ordinance No. 31859, Ordinance No. 31780, Ordinance No. 31913, previously approved on August 12, 2020, February 24, 2021, and June 23, 2021, respectively,   which abandoned portions of Winnetka Avenue (formerly Earle Street), located near the intersection of Fort Worth and Winnetka Avenues, to Paul V. Toler and Donna Toler and Worth Trinity, LLC, and is assigned to the new owner 1030 FWA Owner LP, to extend the final replat from 30 months to 36 months - Revenue: General Fund $5,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
